parameters:
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] Hmm, let's see~n. Even if you ask me to teach you, I'm not sure
what to teach~n. It's a bit late to go over the basics now, isn't
it~n.

\C[27][Rade]\C[0] You have some talent, you know~n. You're also good at applied
magic~n. But you're still a maggot~n.
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] A way for a maggot to stop being a maggot, huh~n.

\C[27][Rade]\C[0] Even if a maggot tries hard, it'll just become a caterpillar in
the end~n. Kyahaha~n!

\C[27][Rade]\C[0] (Is it something like a magical cast that's forced on her?
Normally it's invisible...?)
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] (This girl... she has put chains of restraint on herself...?)
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] (Why does she have these chains of restraint...)
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] (Is she not just any blue mage's daughter?)

\C[27][Rade]\C[0] (She seems to be limiting her own magic with these chains so
others won't notice. I can barely see the chains binding her... a
cross of chains on herself...)

\C[27][Rade]\C[0] (A melody that could be taken as madness... This tune... Has she
been restraining herself with these chains for a long time without
others realizing? For what purpose...)

\C[27][Rade]\C[0] (Those chains would require considerable resolve to wear. Even
high-ranking mages would hesitate to use such restraining magic
chains... What happened to this girl?)

\C[27][Rade]\C[0] (It's common for those with some talent to wear magical armor to
show off or to increase their defense. I've seen plenty of such people
rot away, but this girl's chains are different, they're abnormal. The
chains are more suppressive... rather than blue magic, I'm more
curious about this girl's melody of madness.)

\C[27][Rade]\C[0] (Originally, those chains might have been intended to enhance
magical abilities, but it seems they are now used to suppress
something. Why did it come to this? It's as if the chains themselves
have emotions. I can't tell if it's hatred or resentment, but they're
suppressing negative emotions...?)
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] (It was troublesome being followed by this girl.)

\C[27][Rade]\C[0] (Interesting. I can somewhat understand why Regnus is interested
in her.)
\I[79]Luuna's magical defense power has temporarily increased significantly.

\C[27][Rade]\C[0] I've temporarily significantly increased your magical defense
power~n.

\C[27][Rade]\C[0] There's nothing I need to teach you~n. Your abilities have
already blossomed, after all~n. In your own way~n.

\C[27][Rade]\C[0] If there's anything~n, it's that I'll teach you one of my
spells~n.
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] You're a blue mage, right~n? Then steal my magic for yourself~n.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Eh, I'm going to steal Rade-san's magic?

\C[27][Rade]\C[0] That's the quickest way~n. For a maggot to evolve into a
caterpillar~n.

\C[27][Rade]\C[0] But~n, you need defensive power to withstand my magic~n. Of
course, I'll hold back a bit~n. That's why I temporarily boosted your
magical defense power~n.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Understood. I will learn Rade-san's magic!

\C[27][Rade]\C[0] Then~, here I go~n. I'll play around a bit since it's a special
occasion~n. Kyahaha-n!
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] Peshi Peshi Peshi Peshi! Now, let's get started~n!

\C[27][Rade]\C[0] Hey~! Wait a minute~! This setting~n, isn't one where you can
beat me in the game, is it~n? This is a bug~! A malfunction~n!
